Azure VPN Gateway enables secure communication between on-premise networks and Azure VNets using encrypted tunnels.

Types include:

* Site-to-Site VPN
* Point-to-Site VPN

For example, employees can securely access Azure resources from their office network.

A real-life use case is hybrid cloud architecture where on-premise systems connect to Azure.

Another example is remote employees accessing corporate resources securely.

VPN Gateway ensures secure connectivity over the internet.
